description: Jack and Samuel are both big muscle guys who absolutely look great together. There was a bit of competition as to who was stronger…comparing muscles, teasing each other, joking around…just like old workout buddies. Jack really enjoyed the company, “I wouldn’t mind a workout partner everyday doing these…glad I got this one!” Samuel clearly did too, “I know what else I could do every day with you!” He was really excited to bottom for the first time, “I got a virgin little asshole, so we’re gonna see what we can do with it!” Lucky for him, Jack was there to assist! There’s nothing like two burly men going at it in a battle of the Titans!
title: Jack & Samuel: Bareback
